text:
A game for the #mathartchallenge today: Sprouts. üå±

-Start with some dots.
-Connect any 2 of them w/ a curve/line.
-Along that curve, add another dot.
-Curves can loop to same dot, but no dot can have more than 3 connections. 
-Take turns, and the last player to draw wins. https://t.co/oXU6meuFXl
